Fabian Forte https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fabian_Forte 0 Fabiano Anthony Forte (born February 6, 1943), professionally known as Fabian, is an American singer and actor. Forte rose to national prominence after performing several times on American Bandstand. He became a teen idol of the late 1950s and early 1960s. Eleven of his songs reached the Billboard Hot 100 listing. Fabiano_Anthony_Forte ( born February_6_,_1943 ) , professionally_known as Fabian , is an_American_singer_and_actor .
